{"tid":1232971,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"諗到一個方法收TVB皮+落林鄭面","createTime":"2019-06-16T17:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T13:30:33.000Z","uid":3549,"like":8,"dislike":81,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b44d1b1802ffe7508e2dfe17b94e26cf28c726cf","tid":1232971,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:02:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對和平理性非暴力</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每年7月1號咪有回龜升旗儀式既<br />\n<br />\n我既靈感係來自：<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20141002/large/02la3p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20141002%2Flarge%2F02la3p1.jpg&h=7fe369af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但剩係交叉手 背對國旗 唔唱<br />\n冇咩用處 仲有少柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">方法係</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/874763/org/09f48582b82a76252dbeeefe5bb859f8.jpg/Frdhx6OotFPDVxoAXttOLINJIWtKLN1057YPNee2DzU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F874763%2Forg%2F09f48582b82a76252dbeeefe5bb859f8.jpg%2FFrdhx6OotFPDVxoAXttOLINJIWtKLN1057YPNee2DzU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1cf87e0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/qF2v_j_FV2EZWiAhfcyg4AEmcow=/0x6:650x372/1600x900/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/47151428/middle_finger_emoji.0.0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2FqF2v_j_FV2EZWiAhfcyg4AEmcow%3D%2F0x6%3A650x372%2F1600x900%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_image%2Fimage%2F47151428%2Fmiddle_finger_emoji.0.0.jpg&h=22fb3997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">-對住國旗舉高中指<br />\n-唱粗口版國歌 詳見<span style=\"color: red;\">#2</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夠低成本啦 唔駛衝 唔駛犯法 <br />\n係要你早起身同大聲唱咋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱晒和理非 (除非你係非粗口)<br />\n日日俾政府大力抽插 呻吟大聲d都唔得？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>成效</strong></span></span><br />\nTVB冇理由唔影，我睇下你係咪mute左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又可以睇下林奠咩表情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲可以俾外國睇下中國同香港政府有幾柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唱完跟手去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d203dfdefc1bc9678392698670a289a04f4dac","tid":1232971,"uid":3549,"like":28,"dislike":15,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:03:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歌詞:</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n屌你! 屌你老母個大臭閪!<br />\n屌你老母臭閪, 屌你老母個大臭閪!<br />\n屌你老母臭閪 屌你老母臭閪,<br />\n屌你老母 屌你老母 屌你老母閪. 屌你! 屌你! 屌你!<br />\n屌你老母臭閪, 屌你老母臭閪 屌你!<br />\n屌你老母個臭閪 屌你! 屌你! 屌鳩你!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n改良自:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j7bqKpcLMF0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dj7bqKpcLMF0&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=1240ae4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j7bqKpcLMF0</a>"},{"pid":"2ec3a905b2559e7db952e0f867ca82599eed68fd","tid":1232971,"uid":3549,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:04:44.000Z","msg":"可能有人問會唔會收唔到音<br />\n200萬人個個大聲都收唔到 我都冇野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係阿 你呢200萬人唔係以為616行完就算下話?<br />\n只要到時唔係得連登幾丁友(好似塞地鐵咁得10幾個)<br />\n收撚爆TVB個mic阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebcd841aefa7d553e4c7ee059e5c3ebbe6499c3","tid":1232971,"uid":104502,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:06:20.000Z","msg":"國歌法未過好做"},{"pid":"878b4e22c9008048ca0a431a2cb57142029f12fd","tid":1232971,"ui